.Dd June 2, 2026
.Dt SO 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm so
.Nd order songs by Matroska tags
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Ar field ...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
reads paths or song references from standard input, expands paths to Matroska
chapters, orders the songs by metadata, and writes song references to standard
output.
.Pp
A song reference has the form
.Ar path Ns # Ns Ar chapter-id .
When an input line is only a path,
.Nm
expands all chapters in that file.
.Pp
If no fields are specified, songs are ordered by
.Cm album
and then
.Cm # .
.Sh FIELDS
Fields are
.Cm date ,
.Cm orig-date ,
.Cm artist ,
.Cm title ,
.Cm genre ,
.Cm album ,
.Cm # ,
and
.Cm disc .
.Pp
The
.Cm #
and
.Cm disc
fields are ordered numerically.
Other fields are ordered case-insensitively.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr sf 1 ,
.Xr sp 1 ,
.Xr sq 1
